These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
House: palace, farmhouse, wooden
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, orchid, lily
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, june, february
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, bird
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the skateboard is the german##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the wooden house is between the italian and the farmhouse house##2
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person who growslily is the colombian##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| House      | farmhouse    | wooden   | palace           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Flower         | orchid    | lily  | begonia        |
| Birthday           | october | june   | february      |
| Pet   | guinea-pig        | bird    | chinchilla       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Transport         | skateboard     | taxi | jet-ski |

