There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, baking, cooking
House: craftsman, colonial, wooden
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, amaryllis
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, pall-mall, baccarat
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, go
 1. the baccarat-smoker is the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the baccarat-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 4. the person playing canasta is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the craftsman house##1
 7. the colonial house is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the wooden house##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Hobby   | video-games  | cooking  | baking     |
| House   | wooden       | colonial      | craftsman         |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | azalea   | lily    |
| Cigar           | davidoff        | baccarat      | pall-mall         |
