City: paris, new-york, rome
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, poker
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, writer
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, motorbike
 1. the person eating kale is the dressmaker##1
 2. the person playing poker is the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the dressmaker##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person who likes white is between the person playing snooker and the person traveling to rome##2
 8. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the dressmaker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
10. the writer is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the person playing snooker is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
