 2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growsdaisy and the havana-smoker##2
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growsorchid and the futuristic house##2
 7. the person driving the bike is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person traveling to miami##2
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the engineer is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
