The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
City: nizza, prague, liverpool
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, pall-mall, oliveros
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, dressmaker, firefighter
3 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, billiard
 1. the firefighter is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person playing billiard is between the person who likes brown and the person traveling to nizza##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the police-officer##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing snooker##1
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Color      | brown | ebony      | aquamarine      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| City   | prague  | liverpool     | nizza |
| Cigar           | dunhill        | oliveros | pall-mall     |
| Job         | police-officer    | firefighter | dressmaker   |
| Game     | monopoly        | billiard        | snooker   |

