.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, marigold
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, pop, reggae
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, domino
3 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, hamster
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, azaleasy, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, swisher, baccarat
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the owner of the snake##2
5. the fan of reggae is between the owner of the hamster and the person playing domino##2
6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
8. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
9. the person watching azaleasy movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Flower      | azalea      | aconite      | marigold       |
| Music-Genre          | pop      | reggae    | gospel   |
| Game         | domino    | mah-jongg     | billiard     |
| Pet           | snake    | mouse | hamster   |
| Movie-Genre   | azaleasy    | mystery    | epic       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Cigar     | swisher       | cain | baccarat |

