The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, designer, firefighter
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
There are 3 different nationalities: american, brazilian, german
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the brazilian is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the german is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the firefighter is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person who likes amber is between the person who growsdaffodil and the old-henry-smoker##2
6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is the firefighter##1
9. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
