3 different games are played: scrabble, whist, chess
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, disaster, adventure
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the art-deco house is between the person traveling to paris and the person watching adventure movies##2
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the cottage house is the person who growsamaryllis##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
9. the person playing whist is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| City      | miami    | edinburgh       | paris      |
| Flower          | amaryllis   | sunflower   | zinnia  |
| House           | cottage  | art-deco | townhouse    |
| Game   | scrabble   | whist     | chess  |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure     | western        | disaster |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | cycling  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 